{quote}There are many factors impacting the visibility (and editability) of a field. I have had several cases where I made sure a screen included a field, only to find out the field was still not shown, or shown but read-only. Fiddling with screen schemes, screen definitions, field configurations, and field configuration schemes usually worked out, but there was no clear route, and no clear winner in what eventually caused the desired effect.{quote}

I agree that JIRA is very complex and it can be difficult to ascertain why a field is visible/hidden or editable/read-only. We should create an FAQ that summarises the reasons why a field might be visible/hidden or editable/read-only, linking to the relevant documentation.

